Class MedicationRequestDataManager

java.lang.Object
management.MedicationRequestDataManager
All Implemented Interfaces:
DataManager<Medication,String>
public class MedicationRequestDataManager extends Object implements DataManager<Medication,String>
A DataManager for Medical Request that implements interface DataManager Collect data from CSV file with BufferedReader and write back to CSV file with BufferedWriter for the data collected for the ID of medication in String Holds all the data type MedicalBill
